Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] If anyone tries anything other than\Nwhat I’ve ordered,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantle is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have one hour to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:02:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you live up to\Nthe title I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Elm] Of course he's not gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- So what, he's bluffing?\NWith the whole city?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- It may finally push\Nthe kids to see reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a squad of drones in standby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to drop the payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- I believe I was clear in the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If they give me a reason, I'm gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,remove Mantle from the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how we save Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- You call this saving Atlas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing Salem's job for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could work\Ntowards something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you're throwing it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you don't shut your mouth,\NI'm going to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- If this is what gets\Nthe children to cooperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't like this either,\Nbut the top priority is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you even believe what\Nyou're saying anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do any of you believe in anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to wear this rank with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see it for what it really is:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- You want a collar? Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw this traitor in the brig
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, Ironwood wants Penny,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise, Mantle is done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how do we stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Qrow and Robyn are still in his custody,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and May said that Atlas security drones
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,are watching the crater,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're trapped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- And Salem isn't going to stay gone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- So then, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If Miss Hero with all the answers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have an answer, then we have ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, then why don't just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can we please just\Ngive each other a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Emerald's not with Salem anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ozpin is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this doubt and worry and distrust,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't getting us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then nothing has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the exact same\Nplace we were yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Arguing over what to do while
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the kingdom waits to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,glad you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I boost you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't apologize. I got\Nhurt doing what I always do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,just another ditsy move from Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Th-that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to be a team,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but that didn't matter to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When things went wrong you pushed us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You shove people out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to feel\Nthings that are hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be apologizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-when we lost Oscar and\Nthings got difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so... angry, at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For not being as good as the Ace Ops,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for what happened at Robyn's rally,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for losing the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I just\Nfocused on working harder,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,getting stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that we,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I, wouldn't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,my biggest failing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,was as a teammate and as a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah ha! Ha ha! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All water under the bridge, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!`I'm uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna go see if Klein\Nneeds any help with Penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ren,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So we failed as a team, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we succeed as a team too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- I was the one holding us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Jaune,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All I do is make dumb jokes\Nand smash things with a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- What? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- You put everything you\Nhave into what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You support everyone around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you help without worrying\Nabout how it might hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what I love about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- When my mom ran from the Grimm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and left me behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We became Ren and Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I realized on this mission apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who "Just Nora" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I'm ever going to find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then I have to do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've always loved you, Lie Ren,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and that pretty head on your shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,seems like its it's doing a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still got to get mine's sorted out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,before I can be the partner you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's definitely okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Boop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- You get those hallway cameras on a loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's really gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not if we stop him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- There might be a better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm telling you there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, this isn't just about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm going straight up to the academy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am ending this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Or we fail and people get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- He deserves this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been hurting for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's stop pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that what you're trying to do here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is for anyone but yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Clover was a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You respected him, but I gotta tell ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the better Huntsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because you're the\None who walked away,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're the one who was\Nfighting for what was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go telling me that's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know, that giant hound kicked
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,us around like we were nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But Blake said you and the Schnees managed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to take it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Still having to one-up your big sis, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did she tell you what\Nit was? Underneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know what that means then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wouldn't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's what happened to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- When I saw its eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Salem used to kill\Npeople with silver eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,like Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's always wanted me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would that change unless,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when she met Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,she learned she could do something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- We shouldn't lie to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasted our time getting Amity up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking help would come, but it didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and Amity fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- You were being optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, blind optimism isn't great
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but no optimism means we already lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We need hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to take risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- But mine didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- It still got a warning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, they're not called sure things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they're called risks, and\Nin case you didn't notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my plan for Mantle didn't work either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But we got Oscar back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and did a lot more that\Nwas never in the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom took a risk the day she left,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't think,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it went\Nthe way she wanted it to,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's still my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can no longer be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I must open the vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I do not want...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- I must open the vault
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and self-terminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- I must
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,open the vault,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and self-terminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make sure the power goes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a part of you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were only a machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you never could've fought\Nback for this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaune! Boost her Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did... I stop the virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've got an Aura, Penny,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,our friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,not a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Emerald] I think you're wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I highly doubt you're in\Nthe same place you started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I mean, yeah, y-you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,have been getting your asses kicked,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,some of that, my fault, but like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you're at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna take hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm just going to be super pissed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,if you all finally decide to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment I switch sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Switch sides, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Or like, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you all wouldn't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I really think Ozpin would\Nlike to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- I was recently reminded\Nof an old fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A young girl flees the\Nconsequences of a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to a magical place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But, having never learned\Nfrom her initial failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,she only succeeds in spreading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have trusted you with the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and should never have run\Nthe day you discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was rough
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think after everything\Nthat's happened here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Trust is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- And I hope it's a risk\Nyou can take on me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can still feel it fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't just keep amping her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- And we can't keep Ironwood waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guys, she has to go to the vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's actually a risk\Nwe haven't considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- She'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- The academy entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Penny comes alone.
